Package: SampleSizeDiagnostics
Type: Package
Title: Choosing Sample Size for Evaluating a Diagnostic Test
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mohamed Kamal
Maintainer: Mohamed Kamal <mohamed.kamal@57357.org>
Description: This package provides a function to calculate the sample size needed for evaluating a diagnostic test based on sensitivity, specificity, prevalence, and desired precision.
